rows.label: tlk47100161_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I've been practicing salvaging so
I can be like Rex, but I'm not
having much luck with diving...

rows.label: tlk47100161_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Like, when I start to go deep,
I hear this ringing noise in my
ears and it feels horrible...

rows.label: tlk47100161_02_msg0003
rows.name:
But I'm a dab hand at filling the
cylinders with gas! I can fill 'em
right to the brim, no problem!

rows.label: tlk47100161_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Someone even said I was better than
old man Trope at the cylinder shop!
Think I might help out there sometime!
